SubItem.Name: Errorcode
SubItem.Comment: -Status:4 0x4806:"Port inactive" or "Non IO-Link mode" 0x4807:"Non device" or "IO-Power off" or "Communication Module Error" 0x4808:"Communication error" or "Device compare error" -Status:5 Upper byte(1byte) : IO-Link Error Code Lower byte(2byte) : IO-Link Additional Code

SubItem.Name: Timeout

IO-LinkマスタのIO-Linkデバイスからのレスポンス監視時間

SubItem.Name: Sequence No
